# Basic hardened sshd_config generated by Ansible
Port 22
Protocol 2
PermitRootLogin no
PasswordAuthentication no
PermitEmptyPasswords no
ChallengeResponseAuthentication no
UsePAM yes
X11Forwarding no
LogLevel VERBOSE
AcceptEnv LANG LC_*
Subsystem sftp /usr/lib/openssh/sftp-server

# keep other default directives as-is